wikipedia_page.main: Dakota Lili-Joa Ditcheva (born 1999) is a British Muay Thai champion. She was part of the British team that won International Federation of Muaythai Amateur World Championships in Jönköping, Sweden. She is three-time world champion and Daily Mirror and Sport England Pride of Sports Young Sportsperson of the Year.

response: After a win against Dakota Ditcheva, she faced Monica Santos for the ISKA world flyweight title. She won the fight in the third round by KO.
